data.description: Enjoy the Heart of the City in this beautiful luxury townhouse. Quality craftsmanship and updates throughout. Spacious kitchen with stainless appliances, granite countertops, huge center island, stone backsplash, and maple cabinets. Open floor plan with 9 ft ceilings on all levels. Primary suite has private full bath with separate tub and shower and walk-in closet. Finished basement with additional 4th bedroom. Maintenance-free deck and many other features you have to see to appreciate. Walk to dining, shops, parks, and all the entertainment in the Heart of the city.
